data.description: Don't miss a rare opportunity to own a home in Snapper Creek! This 2 story corner unit, with lake view, has a family room converted into 3rd bedroom on 1st floor, 2 full standing showers, accordion shutters throughout, all big ticket items have been taken care of: roof & AC are only 2 years old, new washer & dryer, newly painted exterior and fence, new pavers & artificial grass outside, a shed and covered patio. Community is perfect for a family with tons of amenities, 2 assigned parking spaces, gated security with guard and a low HOA WITH RESERVES. Conveniently located to turnpike, shops, restaurants and more. Showings only on Saturday 4/20 from 11-3pm!
